OL,3,C'Inside you're dying': 6,000-plus
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse cases against men
OL,5,Crecorded
OL,7,FSome readers may find the details of
OL,8,Fthis report distressing.
OL,10,FBy Jordan Moore
OL,12,FDomestic abuse cases against males in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland are on the rise.
OL,15,FPSNI figures obtained exclusively by
OL,16,FUTV show there were 6,321 cases in
OL,17,F2023, up from 3,721 in 2014. That is
OL,18,Froughly 17 every single day.
