OL,3,C'Inside you're dying': 6,000-plus
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse cases against men
OL,5,Crecorded
OL,7,FTwo victims from the North West spoke
OL,8,Fout to help give a voice to the
OL,9,Fthousands of victims.
OL,11,FWe have changed both their names and
OL,12,Fhave hidden their identities.
OL,14,FMark (not his real name) was in an
OL,15,Fabusive relationship for more than 20
OL,16,Fyears. He says he remembers days going
OL,17,Fto work and wearing long sleeve tops
OL,18,Fto hide the marks from his co-workers
OL,19,Fand even lying to his children when
OL,20,Fthey asked him how he got his cuts and
OL,21,Fbruises.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
