OL,3,C'Inside you're dying': 6,000-plus
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse cases against men
OL,5,Crecorded
OL,7,FMark said: "I've been kicked, punched,
OL,8,Fscratched, I've been hit with plates
OL,9,Fand scalded with tea."
OL,11,FDespite his suffering, it took Mark
OL,12,Ftwo decades to finally speak out: "You
OL,13,Ffeel a lot of shame for something that
OL,14,Fis beyond your control, it is a lonely
OL,15,Fplace to be.
OL,17,F"It's not something men openly talk
OL,18,Fabout or discuss because it really is
OL,19,Fa kind of, 'catch yourself on', 'man
OL,20,Fup' or you try and laugh it off, when
OL,21,Fdeep inside you are really dying."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
