OL,4,Cdomestic abuse cases against men
OL,5,Crecorded
OL,7,FJames (not his real name) suffered
OL,8,Ffrom anxiety and depression, brought
OL,9,Fon from years of domestic abuse. He
OL,10,Fsaid it is crucial that men who feel
OL,11,Flost seek the help they require: "It
OL,12,Fhas been a huge help for me anyway,
OL,13,Fbeing able to open up in a safe space
OL,14,Fand with no judgement. It was
OL,15,Fdefinitely paramount for my journey
OL,16,Fanyway, without a shadow of a doubt.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
