OL,3,C'Inside you're dying': 6,000-plus
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse cases against men
OL,5,Crecorded
OL,7,F"Throughout the decades, you have
OL,8,Falways had to be the man, we just need
OL,9,Fto learn to open up a wee bit more, be
OL,10,Fin touch with our emotions and
OL,11,Fcommunicate a lot better. Do not
OL,12,Fsuffer in isolation, get out there and
OL,13,Fsource the right help."
OL,15,FThe increase in domestic abuse cases
OL,16,Fcomes at a time when funding for men's
OL,17,Fmental health services is being cut.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
