OL,3,C'Inside you're dying': 6,000-plus
OL,4,Cdomestic abuse cases against men
OL,5,Crecorded
OL,7,FAlex Anderson was a councillor for
OL,8,FMen's Action Network, a charity which
OL,9,Fhelped men in the North West for 30
OL,10,Fyears: "Our agency has had to close,
OL,11,Ftemporarily, because of funding
OL,12,Fissues. An agency which has saved the
OL,13,Flives of men over those 30 years
OL,14,Fwhatever the issue may be, not just
OL,15,Fdomestic abuse.
OL,17,F"There needs to be that funding or we
OL,18,Fcannot offer a service."
OL,20,FDespite the fall in funding, awareness
OL,21,Fis being raised.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
