OL,4,Cdomestic abuse cases against men
OL,5,Crecorded
OL,7,FMarches have taken place in Belfast
OL,8,Frecently in support of male victims of
OL,9,Fdomestic abuse and Chief
OL,10,FSuperintendent Lindsay Fisher from the
OL,11,FPSNI's Public Protection branch had a
OL,12,Fclear message for victims and abusers:
OL,13,F"Around 30% of our victims that come
OL,14,Fforward are male, for me that's where
OL,15,Fwe speak to the perpetrators.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
