OL,7,F"They are thinking that it is
OL,8,Facceptable but they are also thinking
OL,9,Fthat they are not going to be caught.
OL,10,FPerpetrators can't live under the
OL,11,Fcover of darkness when it comes to
OL,12,Fdomestic abuse because police are
OL,13,Fshining a light on that."
